parser

Class SlideshowData

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.SlideshowData

  • public class SlideshowData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a new object of type SlideshowData. It contains the slideshow's title, holds all the document information and default settings, and a list containing all the SlideData objects.
    Version:
    2.1
    Author:
